{"about_the_game":"Sok-stories is a fun and accessible way to make, play and share games.<br><br>Draw an object, drag it onto the canvas, and add rules to make a game. Upload your best stories to the library and play and rate other people's creations, or share your game with your friends via a weblink!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>fun and easy drawing style<br></li><li>rule system (no programming!)<br></li><li>rooms and transitions<br></li><li>easy uploading and updating games<br></li><li>play and rate other people's games<br></li><li>play your game in-browser at a dedicated website<br></li><li>embed your game and put it on your website!</li></ul><br>The rule system allows for crafting systems, animations, random generation and much more, all without typing code. Delve as deep as you want into the possibilities, and have fun making games!<br><br><i>Thanks to Now Play This festival in London for commissioning sok-stories!</i><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210010/extras/about.png?t=1639495891\" /><br>Sokpop makes a new game every two weeks!<br>Subscribe for 3$ per month at ","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"My First Story","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1210010/fc6217f99948e0e504456cd0e5b22d88e1c98765.jpg"},{"name":"Story Critic","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1210010/ab804b8ae609ae4d6a49cc3e1cb7504674b9ee4e.jpg"},{"name":"Story Connaisseur","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1210010/11cf13476418e807c4736b122bf0f5ffcec7b3b8.jpg"}],"total":3},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1639495891","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1210010/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1639495891","capsule_image":"https://shared.akam